# .gitignore — idea-to-production marketplace
#
# Surgical, not blanket. .claude/ holds BOTH tracked assets (agent-memory/) and
# runtime cruft — only the runtime files are ignored below.
# Inspection reports are tracked ONLY when generated at the repo root (a leading /)
# to leave archived copies under docs/historical/ addable.

# --- Claude Code harness runtime (per-machine / per-session, never shared) ---
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/scheduled_tasks.json
.claude/cache/
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- Marketplace self-dogfood + lifecycle runtime artifacts (regenerable/transient) ---
# These appear at the repo root when the marketplace's own scripts run against itself.
/SCORECARD.json
/marketplace-health.json
/IN_PROGRESS.md
/CHECKPOINT_*.md
/*_INSPECTION_REPORT.md
# Generated adversarial-review verdict artifacts (pr-review / i2p-review write these to the project root)
/PR_REVIEW.md
/I2P_REVIEW.md
# Lifecycle runtime state written by i2p/operate/foundry skills when dogfooded against this repo
/.i2p/

# --- ComfyUI model-survey artifacts (large/regenerable rasters; catalog/journal/pdf stay tracked) ---
/comfyui-experiment/images/
/comfyui-experiment/thumbs/
/comfyui-experiment/contact-sheets/
/comfyui-experiment/.catalog-raw.pdf

# --- image-craft-study artifacts (large/regenerable rasters; catalogs/ledgers stay tracked) ---
/image-craft-study/craft/images/
/image-craft-study/craft/thumbs/
/image-craft-study/craft/contact-sheets/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
*~
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/

# --- Language tooling (defensive: plugins drive local node/python test runs) ---
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
coverage/
.coverage
*.log
.playwright-mcp/
_render_*.html

# Workflow helper scripts (local, not shipped)
.claude/wf-*.js
.vite/
